{"tid":2103132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今增至少20宗初步確診　科大實驗室疑有職員染疫","createTime":"2020-07-11T03:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:02:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf1b0df93a975ace7f24865ce15f60a4658dee7","tid":2103132,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"消息指，今日(11日)新增至少20宗初步確診個案，大部分為本地感染，包括科大一間實驗室有職員確診，校方稍後將會公布消息。現時香港確診個案累計1404宗。<br />\n據悉，該實驗室位於科大鄭裕彤樓6樓「Biotechnology Research Institute」，校方已封鎖現場，正在相關處所進行消毒，並安排同一實驗室其他人員作病毒檢測及隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200711/photo/bkn-20200711112421549-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200711114631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200711112421549-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200711114631&h=e327b193&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1401f99b57a9bed34e1a43cfb3e5f765449456","tid":2103132,"uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"支那UST"},{"pid":"318c0b52230616200ba94cc7d168cc356b13f6c0","tid":2103132,"uid":39710,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次好似爆得幾勁"},{"pid":"f4140c02f66ffb6afa2a9a283025218724b391e1","tid":2103132,"uid":152705,"like":5,"dislike":16,"sc